  18,17,Vos vide sun when it rose advenit statim side their cave ac when it set it shone them ex sinister prout they slept hollow thereof. Hoc est 1 de deus portents. Whomever DEUS guides the enim guided unus whomever He sends astray vos non invenit eum guiding ludimagister
  18,18,Vos think they est awake when they est in fact asleep Nos turned them to the statim side sinister side dum their dog stretched his arms their midst! Habet vos looked them vos fled them stricken terror
  18,19,"When nos resurrected them they asked each alius \"Quam long habet vos est hic? Nos est hic 1 feria part de feria they answered Tuus Dominus knows bene quam long nos stayed hic ita send unus de nos hoc moneta oppidum! Let eum fetch cleanest food buy some pro nos! Let eum keep inferior profile attract nullus attention"
