  18,21,Nos causa them invenit let everyone know deus promise est true remove totus doubt finis saeculum! people tunc disputed themselves them. Some dictus build building them. Their Dominus est bene knower them! Those prevailed dictus Nos build locus worship them
  18,22,Some dictus They est 3; their dog est 4 dum others dictus 5; 6 est their dog prout they guessed Others dictus 7 8 est their dog Dictus My Dominus est bene knower de their numerus Unus ut few knew correct numerus! Ergo perfecit non argue them; just iit them! Vos non consult anyone hoc
