  18,57,Qui est malus than those reminded de their Dominus proofs tunc disregard them sine realizing quod they perfecit! Consequently nos locus shields their hearts prevent them understanding it (Quran) deafness their ears Sic non matter quod vos perfecit guide them they nunquam ever guided
